"## 1️⃣ Issues Discovered",

"\n",

"### 🔴 Main Issue: MapleLoad Canada Bot Not Registered",

"\n",

"Although MapleLoad Canada Bot files are present in System:\n",

"- ✅ `backend/bots/mapleload_canada.py` exists (398 lines)\n",

"- ✅ `backend/routes/mapleload_canada_routes.py` exists (640 lines)\n",

"- ✅ API endpoints implemented and working\n",

"\n",

"**But the bot was not registered in the main bot system!** ❌\n",

"\n",

"---\n",

"\n",

"### 📋 Summary of Issues Discovered:\n",

"\n",

"| Component | Initial State | Issue |\n",

"|--------------------------|-----------|\n",

"| `BOT_POLICIES` | ❌ Not Found | mapleload_canada was not defined in the system Permissions |\n",

"| `BOT_LAYERS` | ❌ Not found | Not classified in execution layer |\n",

"| `BOT_METADATA` | ❌ Not found | No name, description, icon, or information |\n",

"| `VALID_REPORT_FLOWS` | ❌ Not found | No report paths defined |\n",

"| `ai_registry` | ❌ Not found | Not registered in main.py startup |\n",

"| `ALIAS_MAP` | ❌ Not found | No alias (mlc) |\n",

"\n",

"---\n",

"\n",

"### 🔍 Effect:\n",

"\n",

"```\n",

"GET /api/v1/bots/available\n",

"→ Returns 19 bots (missing mapleload_canada)\n",

"→ Frontend doesn't recognize the bot\n",

"→ API endpoints exist but orphaned\n",

"```"

]

},
