"cell_type": "markdown",

"id": "f6846421",

"metadata": {},

"source": [
"## 2️⃣ Implemented Solution\n",

"\n",

"### 📝 Modifications to `backend/ai/roles/bot_permissions.py`\n",

"\n",

"#### 1. Add to BOT_POLICIES:\n",

"\n",

"``python\n",

"\"mapleload_canada\": BotPolicySpec(\n", 
" visible_to_roles={\"admin\", \"subscription_user\", \"super_admin\"},\n", 
" required_features={\"mapleload_access\"},\n", 
"),\n", 
"```\n", 
"\n", 
"#### 2. Add to BOT_LAYERS:\n", 
"\n", 
"```python\n", 
"\"mapleload_canada\": \"execution\",\n", 
"```\n", 
"\n", 
"#### 3. Add to BOT_METADATA (BOT_CAPABILITIES):\n", 
"\n", 
"```python\n", 
"\"mapleload_canada\": {\n", 
" \"name\": \"MLC - MapleLoad Canada\",\n", 
" \"description\": \"Real-time Canadian freight market monitoring and rate analysis.\",\n", 
" \"category\": \"Execution\",\n", 
" \"icon\": \"MLC\",\n", 
" \"color\": \"emerald\",\n", 
" \"tasks\": [\n", 
"\"Monitor Canadian market rates\",\n", 
" \"Daily freight rate reports (6 AM BC)\",\n", 
" \"Hourly rate change detection\",\n", 
" \"Weekly trend analysis\",\n", 
" \"Send rate alerts and notifications\",\n", 
" \"Track 8 major Canadian routes\",\n", 
" ],\n", 
" \"reporting\": {\n",

" \"frequency\": \"hourly\",\n",

" \"receives_from\": [],\n",

" \"sends_to\": [\"freight_bot\", \"mapleload_bot\"],\n",

" },\n",

" },\n",
"```\n",

"\n",
"### 4. Add to VALID_REPORT_FLOWS:\n",

"\n",

"``python\n",

"\"mapleload_canada\": [\"freight_bot\", \"mapleload_bot\"],\n",

"```\n",

"\n",

"---\n",

"\n",
"### 🔧 Modifications to `backend/main.py`\n", 
"\n", 
"#### Bot registration in ai_registry:\n", 
"\n", 
"```python\n", 
"def register_core_bots() -> None:\n", 
"ai_registry.register(GeneralManagerBot())\n", 
"ai_registry.register(FreightBrokerBot())\n", 
"ai_registry.register(OperationsManagerBot())\n", 
"ai_registry.register(FinanceBot())\n", 
"ai_registry.register(DocumentsManagerBot())\n", 
"\n", 
"# Register MapleLoad Canada bot\n", 
"try:\n", 
" from backend.bots. mapleload_canada import MapleLoadCanadaBot\n", 
"ai_registry.register(MapleLoadCanadaBot())\n", 
" log.info(\"[register] MapleLoad Canada bot registered\")\n", 
"except Exception as e:\n", 
"log.warning(f\"[register] Failed to register MapleLoad Canada bot: {e}\")\n", 
"```\n", 
"\n", 
"---\n", 
"\n", 
"### ✨ Modifications to `backend/ai/registry_fill.py`\n", 
"\n", 
"#### Add Alias:\n", 
"\n", 
"```python\n", 
"ALIAS_MAP: Dict[str, str] = {\n", 
" \"maintenance_bot\": \"maintenance_dev\",\n", 
" \"sales_team\": \"sales_bot\",\n", 
" \"security_manager\": \"security_bot\",\n", 
